  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This proposal describes a pilot study aimed at determining whether genetic variations in
      taste receptors determine differential taste tolerability of pediatric medications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a cross-sectional call-back study of taste perception and the relationship between
      taste perception and taste receptor genotype.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
